---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Fitscape Privacy Policy - CoeCode" description="Privacy policy for Fitscape - the RPG fitness tracking app that transforms your health journey into an epic adventure.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-16">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        <span class="text-yellow-400">Fitscape</span> Privacy <span class="text-green-400">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your privacy and health data security are fundamental to our RPG fitness experience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Privacy Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-8 mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-6">Last updated: January 2025</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8 text-white/80">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Our Commitment to Your Privacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              At CoeCode, we believe your health data is deeply personal and should be protected with the highest 
              standards of security and privacy. This privacy policy explains how Fitscape collects, uses, and 
              protects your information as you transform your fitness journey into an epic RPG adventure.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Information We Collect</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-400">Health and Fitness Data</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Fitscape integrates with Apple HealthKit to access your fitness data and convert it into 
              RPG gameplay elements. This data is processed locally on your device and securely 
              synchronized with our servers to enable features like:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Steps, distance, and calories burned (for character progression)</li>
              <li>Workout sessions and active minutes (for XP gains)</li>
              <li>Sleep quality and duration (for stamina recovery)</li>
              <li>Heart rate data (for activity scoring)</li>
              <li>Move goals and achievements (for quest completion)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">Account and Profile Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Email address and display name</li>
              <li>Character customization preferences</li>
              <li>Game progression and achievements</li>
              <li>Equipment and loot collection</li>
              <li>Quest completion history</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-400">Social Features Data</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Friend connections and guild memberships</li>
              <li>Leaderboard rankings and challenges</li>
              <li>Shared achievements and milestones</li>
              <li>In-app messages and social interactions</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-yellow-400">Device and Usage Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Device type, iOS version, and app version</li>
              <li>Location data for dungeon discovery (approximate)</li>
              <li>Push notification preferences</li>
              <li>App usage patterns and feature interaction</li>
              <li>Crash reports and performance data</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-pink-400">Beta Program Information</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Beta signup email and name</li>
              <li>Feedback and bug reports</li>
              <li>Test data and usage analytics</li>
              <li>Early access preferences</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Your data powers the core RPG experience while maintaining the highest privacy standards:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Game Mechanics:</strong> Convert health data into character stats, XP, and progression</li>
              <li><strong>Personalization:</strong> Tailor quests and challenges to your fitness level</li>
              <li><strong>Social Features:</strong> Enable friend connections, guilds, and competitions</li>
              <li><strong>App Improvement:</strong> Analyze usage patterns to enhance features</li>
              <li><strong>Health Insights:</strong> Provide personalized fitness recommendations</li>
              <li><strong>Support:</strong> Provide customer support and technical assistance</li>
              <li><strong>Security:</strong> Detect and prevent fraud or misuse</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Storage and Security</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-400">Local Storage</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Your HealthKit data is processed locally on your device using Apple's secure Health framework. 
              This data never leaves your device in raw form - only computed game values are synchronized.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">Cloud Storage</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Game progress, character data, and social features are stored securely using Firebase with:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>End-to-end encryption in transit and at rest</li>
              <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
              <li>Strict access controls and authentication</li>
              <li>Automatic backups and disaster recovery</li>
              <li>HIPAA-compliant data handling practices</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-400">Data Retention</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Account data retained while account is active</li>
              <li>Health data processed locally, not stored on servers</li>
              <li>Backup data retained for 90 days after account deletion</li>
              <li>Analytics data anonymized after 2 years</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We do not sell your personal or health data to third parties. Limited sharing occurs only for:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Firebase (Google Cloud) for secure data storage</li>
              <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Anonymized usage data to improve app performance</li>
              <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or legal process</li>
              <li><strong>Safety:</strong> To protect user safety or prevent fraud</li>
              <li><strong>With Consent:</strong> When you explicitly authorize sharing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Your Rights and Controls</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-400">Health Data Control</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Control HealthKit permissions in iOS Settings</li>
              <li>Revoke health data access at any time</li>
              <li>Data processing stops immediately when revoked</li>
              <li>Historical game progress preserved</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">Account Management</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Delete your account and all associated data</li>
              <li>Export your game progress and achievements</li>
              <li>Modify privacy settings and preferences</li>
              <li>Control social features and friend connections</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-400">Communication Preferences</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Customize push notification settings</li>
              <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
              <li>Control social notifications and updates</li>
              <li>Manage beta program participation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Location and Movement Data</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Fitscape uses approximate location data to enable dungeon discovery features:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Location access used only for gameplay features</li>
              <li>Approximate location only (within 400m accuracy)</li>
              <li>No precise location tracking or storage</li>
              <li>Location data processed locally on device</li>
              <li>Can be disabled while retaining other features</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Fitscape is intended for users 17 and older due to health data requirements. We do not 
              knowingly collect health or personal information from children under 17. If you are a 
              parent and believe your child has provided information to us, please contact us immediately.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">International Data Transfers</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Your data may be processed in countries outside your residence, including the United States 
              where our servers are located. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect 
              your data according to applicable privacy laws.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We may update this privacy policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. 
              Significant changes will be communicated through the app or email. Your continued use of 
              Fitscape after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you have questions about this privacy policy or our privacy practices, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-4 border border-white/10">
              <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@coecode.io" class="text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-300">privacy@coecode.io</a></p>
              <p><strong>Fitscape Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@coecode.io?subject=Fitscape Privacy" class="text-green-400 hover:text-green-300">support@coecode.io</a></p>
              <p><strong>Address:</strong> Coe Code LLC, Missoula, Montana, USA</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation Links -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
      <a 
        href="/fitscape" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Back to Fitscape
      </a>
      <a 
        href="/fitscape/terms" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Terms of Use
      </a>
      <a 
        href="/connect" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout> 